{"id":"16bebc19f07a6ea0f6cfd7a042da98094154b866","url":"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax","title":"GitHub - pileax-ai/pileax: PileaX is an all-in-one AI knowledge base system. 🍀","site_name":"Buzzing","source":"github.com","byline":null,"excerpt":"PileaX is an all-in-one AI knowledge base system. 🍀 - pileax-ai/pileax","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div data-hpc=\"true\" containertiming=\"hpc\"><article itemprop=\"text\"><p dir=\"auto\"><strong>English</strong> | <a href=\"/pileax-ai/pileax/blob/main/README_zh.md\">简体中文</a></p>\n\n<p dir=\"auto\">PileaX AI: All-in-one AI KnowledgeBase. 🍀</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/actions/workflows/ci.yml\" alt=\"Build Status\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/releases/latest\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/340abb0bae5dc785eea1d28e3d069fd57dc5058ff79c08e2e46ca571ffa2fd16/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f762f72656c656173652f70696c6561782d61692f70696c656178\" alt=\"Latest Release\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/pileax-ai/pileax\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/releases\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d1a7fe217dc8f1f521ead2ce113e8ddcc835ae9647e15cf6716fe44006ddf393/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f646f776e6c6f6164732f70696c6561782d61692f70696c6561782f746f74616c\" alt=\"Downloads\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/pileax-ai/pileax/total\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/badges/shields/pulse\" alt=\"Activity\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ccd119ab73e7cc5db6fdd242b06d0d8b494569b668d9cba7907a6cb3597b887e/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f636f6d6d69742d61637469766974792f6d2f70696c6561782d61692f70696c656178\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/commit-activity/m/pileax-ai/pileax\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/blob/main/LICENSE\" alt=\"License\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1ce8db49ac1c291e1082ceb8a0f85e8a0bc36f1039625fefbdb10e0414fdc4bc/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f6c6963656e73652d4d49542d677265656e3f7374796c653d737175617265\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green?style=square\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://linux.do\" alt=\"LINUX DO\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1466e94cc095e6bca7c1148bc5e2050c21bea050b2407d4476f8387023669957/68747470733a2f2f73686f727475726c2e61742f6767537153\" data-canonical-src=\"https://shorturl.at/ggSqS\"></a>\n</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax#platform-support\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/166f423369d75d02466de47344a3bccbce5d444efe1a28c4f12e279ef21e9412/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f706c6174666f726d2d57696e646f77732532302537432532306d61634f532532302537432532304c696e75782d626c7565\" alt=\"Platforms\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/platform-Windows%20%7C%20macOS%20%7C%20Linux-blue\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax#supported-formats\">\n    <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b21195a49a989987f21983187e519719a042c3c0e6d5dd98671a796f6c4b6c41/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f666f726d6174732d455055422532302537432532304d4f424925323025374325323041575a3325323025374325323046423225323025374325323043425a2532302537432532305044462d7465616c\" alt=\"Supported Formats\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/formats-EPUB%20%7C%20MOBI%20%7C%20AWZ3%20%7C%20FB2%20%7C%20CBZ%20%7C%20PDF-teal\"></a>\n</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">PileaX is a local-first, all-in-one AI knowledge base that integrates AI chat, smart notes, and e-book reading &amp; management. From knowledge creation to application, PileaX helps you build a unified knowledge base and continuously optimizes the AI interaction experience with AI agent technologies.Your data is fully under your control. It supports offline desktop apps and flexibly deployable web apps.</p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Preview</h2><a id=\"user-content-preview\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Preview\" href=\"#preview\"></a></P>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h3 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Main</h3><a id=\"user-content-main\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Main\" href=\"#main\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/8ba3081b234a1675be8c667653c789d26f4a855713bc5f684ee3234d05307916/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f73637265656e73686f74732f6d61696e2e676966\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/8ba3081b234a1675be8c667653c789d26f4a855713bc5f684ee3234d05307916/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f73637265656e73686f74732f6d61696e2e676966\" alt=\"Screenshot\" data-animated-image=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://pileax.ai/screenshots/main.gif\"></a></p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h3 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Reader</h3><a id=\"user-content-reader\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Reader\" href=\"#reader\"></a></P>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h4 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Bookshelf</h4><a id=\"user-content-bookshelf\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Bookshelf\" href=\"#bookshelf\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d6b6064ee829006da1f93ea5688ba362b6b3a1ab37e6f47ea8bf6d577e7d4c4a/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f626f6f6b7368656c662e77656270\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d6b6064ee829006da1f93ea5688ba362b6b3a1ab37e6f47ea8bf6d577e7d4c4a/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f626f6f6b7368656c662e77656270\" alt=\"Screenshot\" data-canonical-src=\"https://pileax.ai/images/en/reading/bookshelf.webp\"></a></p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h4 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Reading view</h4><a id=\"user-content-reading-view\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Reading view\" href=\"#reading-view\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ae70624e901537c628ef053bbe700dcbaf73b2caad42550b2913669e30fe1acc/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f7265616465722d766572746963616c2e77656270\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ae70624e901537c628ef053bbe700dcbaf73b2caad42550b2913669e30fe1acc/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f7265616465722d766572746963616c2e77656270\" alt=\"Screenshot\" data-canonical-src=\"https://pileax.ai/images/en/reading/reader-vertical.webp\"></a>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9a1b6d239587c3d855cddea1656eea6d034d4ab73fbd3871819027e85c4e5942/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f7265616465722d686f72697a6f6e74616c2e77656270\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9a1b6d239587c3d855cddea1656eea6d034d4ab73fbd3871819027e85c4e5942/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f7265616465722d686f72697a6f6e74616c2e77656270\" alt=\"Screenshot\" data-canonical-src=\"https://pileax.ai/images/en/reading/reader-horizontal.webp\"></a></p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h4 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">TOC, Bookmark, Highlight, Annotation and AI</h4><a id=\"user-content-toc-bookmark-highlight-annotation-and-ai\" aria-label=\"Permalink: TOC, Bookmark, Highlight, Annotation and AI\" href=\"#toc-bookmark-highlight-annotation-and-ai\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/610c73c77277541fe00f3eabead345e4e6db1a1d31634c61942a05284c34105e/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f7265616465722e77656270\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/610c73c77277541fe00f3eabead345e4e6db1a1d31634c61942a05284c34105e/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f696d616765732f656e2f72656164696e672f7265616465722e77656270\" alt=\"Screenshot\" data-canonical-src=\"https://pileax.ai/images/en/reading/reader.webp\"></a></p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h4 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">More</h4><a id=\"user-content-more\" aria-label=\"Permalink: More\" href=\"#more\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b899066b041c254ce6844b2c59c11172145692bb3b8ce271deb8fff62e8f428d/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f73637265656e73686f74732f7265616465722e676966\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b899066b041c254ce6844b2c59c11172145692bb3b8ce271deb8fff62e8f428d/68747470733a2f2f70696c6561782e61692f73637265656e73686f74732f7265616465722e676966\" alt=\"Screenshot\" data-animated-image=\"\" data-canonical-src=\"https://pileax.ai/screenshots/reader.gif\"></a></p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Features</h2><a id=\"user-content-features\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Features\" href=\"#features\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\">🚀 <strong>AI Chat</strong> – Your AI assistant, ready to answer questions and tackle tasks. <br>\n📝 <strong>Notes</strong> - Modern Notion-style editor. <br>\n🤖 <strong>Reading</strong> – Build your personal library and enjoy AI-powered reading. <br>\n🌗 Light &amp; Dark mode. <br>\n🆓 MIT Licensed. <br></p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Quick start</h2><a id=\"user-content-quick-start\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Quick start\" href=\"#quick-start\"></a></P>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><a href=\"https://pileax.ai/guide/getting-started\" rel=\"nofollow\">Getting started</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pileax.ai/download\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\">For more detailed information, make sure to check out our <a href=\"https://pileax.ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">documentation</a>. If you encounter any problems or have suggestions, please open an <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/issues/new/choose\">issue</a>.</p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h3 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Desktop</h3><a id=\"user-content-desktop\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Desktop\" href=\"#desktop\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Download desktop application from <a href=\"https://pileax.ai/download\" rel=\"nofollow\">download page</a> or <a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/releases\">release page</a>.</p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h3 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Docker Compose</h3><a id=\"user-content-docker-compose\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Docker Compose\" href=\"#docker-compose\"></a></P>\n<div dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"cd docker\ncp backend.env.example backend.env\n\n# start\ndocker compose up -d\n\n# stop\ndocker compose down\"><pre><span>cd</span> docker\ncp backend.env.example backend.env\n\n<span><span>#</span> start</span>\ndocker compose up -d\n\n<span><span>#</span> stop</span>\ndocker compose down</pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Then, open <a href=\"http://localhost:9610\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://localhost:9610</a> to start.</p>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Contributing</h2><a id=\"user-content-contributing\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Contributing\" href=\"#contributing\"></a></P>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h3 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Community &amp; contact</h3><a id=\"user-content-community--contact\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Community & contact\" href=\"#community--contact\"></a></P>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/issues\">GitHub Issues</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/8QQWYXF8Vd\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord</a></li>\n</ul>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h3 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Contributors</h3><a id=\"user-content-contributors\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Contributors\" href=\"#contributors\"></a></P>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/pileax/graphs/contributors\">\n  <img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c5e229ffacb49a1955d2a18d6927a5ee4ac98b17e8cae6b339248c6fc4081845/68747470733a2f2f636f6e747269622e726f636b732f696d6167653f7265706f3d70696c6561782d61692f70696c656178\" data-canonical-src=\"https://contrib.rocks/image?repo=pileax-ai/pileax\">\n</a>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">Acknowledgements</h2><a id=\"user-content-acknowledgements\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Acknowledgements\" href=\"#acknowledgements\"></a></P>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/langgenius/dify/\">Dify</a>: An open-source platform for developing LLM applications.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/infiniflow/ragflow\">RAGFlow</a>: A leading open-source Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) engine that fuses cutting-edge RAG with Agent capabilities to create a superior context layer for LLMs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/johnfactotum/foliate-js\">foliate-js</a>: Library for rendering e-books in the browser.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/readest/readest\">Readest</a>: An open-source ebook reader designed for immersive and deep reading experiences.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Anxcye/anx-reader\">Anx Reader</a>: A thoughtfully crafted e-book reader for book lovers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pileax-ai/yiitap\">Yiitap</a>: An AI powered, Notion-style WYSIWYG rich-text block-based editor built on top of <a href=\"https://github.com/ueberdosis/tiptap\">Tiptap</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://github.com/ProseMirror/prosemirror\">ProseMirror</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<P dir=\"auto\"><h2 tabindex=\"-1\" dir=\"auto\">License</h2><a id=\"user-content-license\" aria-label=\"Permalink: License\" href=\"#license\"></a></P>\n<p dir=\"auto\">The MIT License (MIT). Please see <a href=\"/pileax-ai/pileax/blob/main/LICENSE\">License File</a> for more information.</p>\n</article></div></DIV>","content_text":"English | 简体中文 PileaX AI: All-in-one AI KnowledgeBase. 🍀 PileaX is a local-first, all-in-one AI knowledge base that integrates AI chat, smart notes, and e-book reading & management. From knowledge creation to application, PileaX helps you build a unified knowledge base and continuously optimizes the AI interaction experience with AI agent technologies.Your data is fully under your control. It supports offline desktop apps and flexibly deployable web apps. Preview Main Reader Bookshelf Reading view TOC, Bookmark, Highlight, Annotation and AI More Features 🚀 AI Chat – Your AI assistant, ready to answer questions and tackle tasks. 📝 Notes - Modern Notion-style editor. 🤖 Reading – Build your personal library and enjoy AI-powered reading. 🌗 Light & Dark mode. 🆓 MIT Licensed. Quick start Getting started Download For more detailed information, make sure to check out our documentation. If you encounter any problems or have suggestions, please open an issue. Desktop Download desktop application from download page or release page. Docker Compose cd docker cp backend.env.example backend.env # start docker compose up -d # stop docker compose down Then, open http://localhost:9610 to start. Contributing Community & contact GitHub Issues Discord Contributors Acknowledgements Dify: An open-source platform for developing LLM applications. RAGFlow: A leading open-source Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) engine that fuses cutting-edge RAG with Agent capabilities to create a superior context layer for LLMs. foliate-js: Library for rendering e-books in the browser. Readest: An open-source ebook reader designed for immersive and deep reading experiences. Anx Reader: A thoughtfully crafted e-book reader for book lovers. Yiitap: An AI powered, Notion-style WYSIWYG rich-text block-based editor built on top of Tiptap & ProseMirror. License The MIT License (MIT). Please see License File for more information.","fetched_at":"2026-07-24T12:36:14.593Z","ok":true}